---

<SiteLayout site="nookienook" canonical="https://thenookienook.com/date-ideas-by-season" title={meta.title} description={meta.description} schema={JSON.stringify(jsonLd)}>
  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>100 Date Ideas by Season</h1>
      <p>Find the perfect date idea for any time of year. We have organized 100 ideas by season, complete with budget estimates and effort levels.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="category-section">
      <h2>Spring Date Ideas</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Embrace the blooming flowers and warmer weather with these 25 spring dates.</p>
      <div class="ideas-grid">
        {springIdeas.map(idea => (
          <div class="idea-card">
            <h3>{idea.name}</h3>
            <p class="idea-desc">{idea.desc}</p>
            <div class="idea-meta">
              <span class="meta-tag">Budget: {idea.budget}</span>
              <span class="meta-tag">Effort: {idea.effort}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="category-section">
      <h2>Summer Date Ideas</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Soak up the sun and long evenings with these 25 summer dates.</p>
      <div class="ideas-grid">
        {summerIdeas.map(idea => (
          <div class="idea-card">
            <h3>{idea.name}</h3>
            <p class="idea-desc">{idea.desc}</p>
            <div class="idea-meta">
              <span class="meta-tag">Budget: {idea.budget}</span>
              <span class="meta-tag">Effort: {idea.effort}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="category-section">
      <h2>Fall Date Ideas</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Get cozy and enjoy the autumn foliage with these 25 fall dates.</p>
      <div class="ideas-grid">
        {fallIdeas.map(idea => (
          <div class="idea-card">
            <h3>{idea.name}</h3>
            <p class="idea-desc">{idea.desc}</p>
            <div class="idea-meta">
              <span class="meta-tag">Budget: {idea.budget}</span>
              <span class="meta-tag">Effort: {idea.effort}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="category-section">
      <h2>Winter Date Ideas</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Stay warm or embrace the snow with these 25 winter dates.</p>
      <div class="ideas-grid">
        {winterIdeas.map(idea => (
          <div class="idea-card">
            <h3>{idea.name}</h3>
            <p class="idea-desc">{idea.desc}</p>
            <div class="idea-meta">
              <span class="meta-tag">Budget: {idea.budget}</span>
              <span class="meta-tag">Effort: {idea.effort}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>What are some good spring date ideas?</h3>
        <p>Great spring dates include visiting a farmers market, hiking, viewing cherry blossoms, or taking an outdoor yoga class.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>What are fun summer dates?</h3>
        <p>Fun summer date ideas involve a beach day, catching a drive-in movie, relaxing at a rooftop bar, or kayaking.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>What are the best fall dates?</h3>
        <p>The best fall dates are apple picking, exploring a haunted house, sitting by a bonfire, or going wine tasting.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>How to plan a winter date?</h3>
        <p>A perfect winter date could be ice skating, going on a hot chocolate crawl, taking a cooking class, or a museum day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card faq-card">
        <h3>How are these date ideas categorized?</h3>
        <p>These 100 date ideas are categorized by season, and each includes a budget estimate and an effort level.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
